    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Journey to distant worlds, where every puzzle is a gateway to the unknown.  Lose yourself in the meditative rhythm of matching tiles, unlocking new experiences as you explore the realms.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unlock Mystical and Alien Realms</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Progress through beautifully crafted realms, each with its own unusual tile sets and atmospheric themes. From tranquil zen spaces to eerie alien worlds, every realm offers a distinct experience.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Puzzle Editor &amp; Steam Workshop Integration</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craft your own puzzles with the intuitive editor and share them on the Steam Workshop. Browse a growing collection of player-made layouts for endless replayability and challenges.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Immersive Music &amp; Visuals</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each realm is brought to life with custom music tracks and striking visuals, creating a deep, immersive atmosphere that evolves with your journey.</p>",
